headline: Weekly Dividend ETF COIW Pays 52 Times Per Year But 100% Return of Capital Raises Red Flags for Retirees
summary: The Roundhill COIN WeeklyPay ETF (NYSEARCA:COIW) offers 52 dividend payments per year, a huge improvement over the quarterly payments of most ETFs, and a newer cohort of monthly yield options.
